        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">永久叫停</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國民警衛隊成員本周在華盛頓遭到槍擊，嫌犯據報導已確認是阿富汗籍。事件發生後，川普先是叫停了阿富汗國民的移民申請，然後更是宣布將永久叫停來自所有「第三世界」國家的移民。他還表示，要驅逐所有成為公共負擔、安全威脅或與西方文明不相容的外國人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">處境危險</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在貸款申請據悉被部分中資銀行拒絕之後，萬科股債續創新低。標普下調了該公司評級。有分析師稱，萬科本周提出債務展期，恐預示其流動性出現螺旋式下降。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拖累經濟</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-29f9a12d-6024-3f38-9daf-5c36c2ce27e4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在日本首相推出疫情以來最大規模刺激計畫之後，該國政府計畫新發行11.7萬億日圓債券、為其籌措資金。但是高市早苗涉台談論引發的中日緊張局勢仍未平息，高盛預計日本旅遊業將因此受到衝擊，從而拖累日本GDP增速。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高度相關</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會12月降息預期重新升溫。而東京通膨超出預期，進一步提振了日本央行加息預期，從而料將支撐日圓兌美元走高預測。鑒於韓元與日圓走勢的相關性升至近20年最高水平，分析師稱，如果聯儲會真的降息，那麼這兩種亞洲貨幣可能聯袂上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">技術故障</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">芝商所駐新加坡發言人稱，因為CyrusOne數據中心出現冷卻問題，芝商所的大宗商品期貨和期權實時交易周五暫停。原油和棕櫚油等多個合約受到了影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-054920258.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-28 14:30:43",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "交易員稱芝商所大宗商品期貨交易暫停",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據關注該平台的交易員透露，芝商所的大宗商品期貨實時交易已經暫停。包括原油和棕櫚油在內的合約，在周五亞洲早盤交易時段受到影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">芝商所未立即回覆彭博的詢問。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題CME Group Commodity Futures Trading Halted, Traders Say</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Hallie Gu、Serene Cheong、Yongchang Chin.</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B1%E8%8A%9D%E5%95%86%E6%89%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%97%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C-035432142.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-28 12:45:44",
